text: KSBU (92.7 FM, "92.7 The Touch") is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Delta, Louisiana. The station is owned by Holladay Broadcasting of Louisiana, LLC, and airs an urban adult contemporary format. The station was assigned the KSBU call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on August 26, 2010. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FCC Public Inspection File for KSBU * Category:Radio stations in Louisiana Category:Radio stations established in 2013 Category:2013 establishments in Louisiana Category:Urban adult contemporary radio stations in the United States Category:Madison Parish, Louisiana
